---
title: Double Bacon, Mushroom & Parmesan Fettuccine with Carrot Salad
description: Just look at how much good stuff is about to go into this dish. Between the tender mushrooms, crispy bacon and tasty
Parmesan, we really don’t know why you’re still reading this. Get started and enjoy every bite of this perfect bowl of pasta!
